{"tid":1449000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「黑警還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:49:42.000Z","uid":302421,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6774e50e3e36787202ad266725bb39fd4300764f","tid":1449000,"uid":302421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:44:45.000Z","msg":"無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpnaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=dfb3a213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpnaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=04884f5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"6b47e64417730ce8d94ed1af2590b67559a422f1","tid":1449000,"uid":302421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:48:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27aa78f349e9acfd748f7a62dd9b3ed99d02c664","tid":1449000,"uid":302421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903f7184a603cef950e03bf5e33cb7ed29c3bf3e","tid":1449000,"uid":302421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c9ae787d742a76e1af24634bf968932c744d276","tid":1449000,"uid":302421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy